WEBVTT

00:00.750 --> 00:01.717
- THERE WAS A VENDING MACHINE

00:01.820 --> 00:04.232
IN THE SCHOOL LAST YEAR,
BUT THEY TOOK IT OUT.

00:04.340 --> 00:05.921
I'M RUNNING FOR STUDENT COUNCIL
PRESIDENT--I'M GOING TO WIN.

00:06.040 --> 00:06.995
I'M GOING TO GET
THE SCHOOL BOARD

00:07.110 --> 00:08.919
TO BRING BACK
THE VENDING MACHINE.

00:09.040 --> 00:10.928
- KRISTINA'S SICK.
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN, SICK?

00:11.040 --> 00:12.268
- I CAN'T YOU ALL THE DETAILS,

00:12.390 --> 00:14.073
AND YOU'RE THE FIRST PERSON
I'M TELLING, SO...

00:14.180 --> 00:15.795
SORRY SOME OF THIS STUFF
IS GONNA FALL ON YOU,

00:15.910 --> 00:18.492
BUT I'M GONNA KEEP ASKING YOU TO
DO SOME OF THESE THINGS FOR ME

00:18.600 --> 00:20.079
BECAUSE
I'M GONNA NEED YOUR HELP.

00:20.190 --> 00:21.976
- MRS. BRAVERMAN,
A LUMPECTOMY,

00:22.090 --> 00:23.978
PERFORMED SOONER
RATHER THAN LATER,

00:24.090 --> 00:25.466
OFFERS THE BEST CHANCE
OF REMISSION.

00:25.570 --> 00:30.086
I HAVE AN OPENING FRIDAY
THE 26TH AT 8:00 A.M.

00:31.200 --> 00:33.020
- [sighs]
- OKAY.

00:33.130 --> 00:35.690
ANY SECOND NOW.

00:37.340 --> 00:40.093
- I'M GOING BACK TO BED.
- NO, NO, WAIT, WAIT.

00:40.210 --> 00:41.962
YOU'RE GONNA MISS IT.
YOU'RE GONNA MISS IT.

00:42.070 --> 00:44.038
IT'S GONNA COME,
I SWEAR TO GOD.

00:44.140 --> 00:46.791
COME ON, IT'LL BE,...
IT'LL BE HERE.

00:46.900 --> 00:48.834
- I'M GOING BACK TO BED.

00:48.940 --> 00:50.316
- OH!

00:50.420 --> 00:53.492
LOOK! THERE.
SHH! NOW, LISTEN.

00:53.600 --> 00:55.010
YOU HEAR THAT?

00:55.120 --> 00:57.566
[water hissing]

01:01.950 --> 01:03.577
- NO.

01:03.680 --> 01:04.886
NO. IT SOUNDS FINE TO ME.

01:04.990 --> 01:05.672
_ OH--
- ZEEK, REALLY.

01:05.780 --> 01:07.407
- CAMILLE, IT'S NOT FINE.

01:07.510 --> 01:10.502
THERE'S LIKE AN AIR SOUND,
YOU KNOW?

01:10.620 --> 01:11.575
- HEY.
- UH-HUH?

01:11.690 --> 01:13.510
- YOU NEED A HOBBY.

01:18.110 --> 01:19.657
[engine rewing]

01:19.760 --> 01:22.342
- SPORTS. THEY'RE AN INCREDIBLE
WAY TO MAKE FRIENDS.

01:22.460 --> 01:23.654
- GREAT WAY.
- I'M STILL IN TOUCH

01:23.770 --> 01:25.044
WITH A NUMBER OF GIRLS
FROM MY SWIM TEAM.

01:25.150 --> 01:26.424
IN FACT,
JUST THE OTHER DAY,

01:26.530 --> 01:28.498
ONE OF THEM SENT ME
A MESSAGE ON FACEBOOK.

01:28.600 --> 01:29.942
- OH!
- AND SPORTS ARE FUN!

01:30.050 --> 01:31.972
- SUPER FUN.
- VIDEO GAMES ARE FUN.

01:32.090 --> 01:34.672
- I KNOW YOU LIKE WATCHING
BASEBALL WITH ME, YOU KNOW.

01:34.780 --> 01:36.293
THAT MIGHT BE SOMETHING
YOU COULD DO.

01:36.400 --> 01:37.708
THAT WAS MY SPORT GROWING UP.
I LOVED IT.

01:37.820 --> 01:40.573
- OR YOU COULD TRY ONE OF
THE SPORTS THAT I DID--

01:40.680 --> 01:42.090
SWIMMING...
- SWIMMING'S GREAT.

01:42.200 --> 01:43.337
- SOCCER.
- GOOD FOR YOUR HEART.

01:43.440 --> 01:44.953
- VOLLEYBALL, TENNIS.

01:45.070 --> 01:46.549
I WAS BRIEFLY COMPETITIVE
IN GYMNASTICS

01:46.650 --> 01:48.231
BEFORE MY GROWTH SPURT.
- ANYWAY--

01:48.340 --> 01:49.022
- PROBABLY NOT. YEAH.
- IT'S YOUR CALL HERE.

01:49.140 --> 01:51.301
YOUR CHOICE.

01:51.420 --> 01:53.342
- SWEET.
THEN I CHOOSE NOTHING.

01:53.450 --> 01:56.339
[game sounds continue]

01:57.630 --> 01:59.621
- NOTHING...
IS NOT AN OPTION.

01:59.740 --> 02:01.526
- BUT YOU JUST SAID
IT WAS MY CHOICE.

02:01.630 --> 02:03.871
- YOU'RE NOT GONNA SIT
ON THIS COUCH EVERY AFTERNOON

02:03.980 --> 02:05.208
PLAYING VIDEO GAMES.

02:05.330 --> 02:07.389
YOU EITHER...PICK A SPORT

02:07.500 --> 02:09.843
OR YOU LEARN TO PLAY
THE VIOLIN.

02:14.750 --> 02:16.889
- FINE.
BASEBALL.

02:16.990 --> 02:19.333
EXCUSE ME.
- FINE.

02:21.340 --> 02:22.580
[game sounds resume]

02:22.690 --> 02:24.510
BASEBALL.

02:25.830 --> 02:28.310
- SO WE JUST WANTED
TO DISCUSS THE SURGERY DATE.

02:28.420 --> 02:29.864
- IS THERE A CONFLICT
WITH THE 26TH?

02:29.970 --> 02:31.346
- NO, MY WIFE JUST HAS...
- WELL, KIND OF, YES.

02:31.460 --> 02:32.859
- A QUESTION ABOUT WHETHER
WE CAN MOVE IT.

02:32.980 --> 02:34.834
- MY SON IS RUNNING FOR
PRESIDENT OF STUDENT COUNCIL,

02:34.940 --> 02:36.350
AND HE HAS ASPERGER'S.

02:36.460 --> 02:38.007
HE JUST STARTED AT A NEW SCHOOL,
AND I NEED TO BE THERE.

02:38.120 --> 02:39.906
I'M THE ROOM MOM THAT DAY.
- I REALIZE THAT MIGHT SOUND

02:40.020 --> 02:41.908
KIND OF ASININE IN THE GREATER
SCHEME OF THINGS...

02:42.020 --> 02:43.772
- IT'S REALLY NOT--
- WHEN'S MY NEXT AVAILABLE?

02:43.880 --> 02:46.394
- YOU HAVE AN OPENING
THE 12TH OF NEXT MONTH.

02:46.510 --> 02:48.717
- DOES THAT WORK FOR YOU,
MRS. BRAVERMAN?

02:48.820 --> 02:50.538
- THAT WOULD BE GREAT.
I COULD BUY MORE TIME,

02:50.650 --> 02:52.368
AND, YOU KNOW,
WORK WITH THE CLASS--

02:52.480 --> 02:54.789
- BUT THAT'S THREE WEEKS.
IS THAT TOO LONG TO PUSH IT?

02:54.890 --> 02:56.266
- LOOK, I'VE ALREADY ADVISED YOU
TO HAVE THE SURGERY

02:56.380 --> 02:58.723
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE,

02:58.830 --> 03:02.038
BUT IF THE 12TH IS THE SOONEST
POSSIBLE DATE FOR YOU,

03:02.140 --> 03:04.483
THEN WE WILL
DO IT ON THE 12TH.

03:04.590 --> 03:06.478
- I FEEL LIKE YOU'RE SAYING
SOONER'S BETTER THAN LATER.

03:06.600 --> 03:08.739
I JUST WANT TO DO THE RIGHT
THING HERE, HONEY.

03:08.840 --> 03:10.933
- ALL RIGHT, MRS. BRAVERMAN,
YOU KNOW, PUSHING SURGERY

03:11.050 --> 03:12.768
BACK A FEW WEEKS IS NOT
THE END OF THE WORLD,

03:12.880 --> 03:14.529
BUT I HAVE A SENSE
THAT YOU'RE THE TYPE OF PERSON

03:14.640 --> 03:17.291
WHO PUTS YOUR FAMILY FIRST
AND YOURSELF LAST.

03:17.400 --> 03:19.459
- THAT'S TRUE.
- WELL, I MEAN, SORT OF--

03:19.570 --> 03:23.745
- YOU HAVE ONE JOB THIS YEAR,
MRS. BRAVERMAN,

03:23.850 --> 03:25.602
AND THAT IS TO FOCUS
ON GE'I'I'ING HEALTHY.

03:25.720 --> 03:27.711
THAT IS THE MOST IMPORTANT
THING FOR YOU

03:27.820 --> 03:29.128
AND FOR YOUR FAMILY.

03:29.240 --> 03:31.708
- OKAY.

03:31.830 --> 03:35.038
- SO...THE 12TH.

03:35.140 --> 03:36.789
- IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

03:39.110 --> 03:40.418
- THE 12TH.

03:41.490 --> 03:44.459
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH,
YEAH, YEAH.

03:44.560 --> 03:46.767
- CHECK, CHECK, CHECK.

03:46.880 --> 03:48.211
- YEAH.

03:48.330 --> 03:49.183
THIS AIN'T NO TRAP MUSIC

03:49.290 --> 03:51.326
NO ILLUSION

03:51.430 --> 03:52.909
CO-SIGN ABUSING

03:53.020 --> 03:54.499
FORCE ACCUSING

03:54.610 --> 03:57.124
THEY INNOCENT,
NEVER DUST UP A FINGERPRINT

03:57.230 --> 03:59.152
THIS THAT DARK SET,
NO LIGHTS

04:00.440 --> 04:01.816
LIFE MEMBERSHIP

04:01.930 --> 04:04.160
REVOKIN' WITH
MY PENMANSHIP...

04:07.350 --> 04:08.419
- [whispers]
HEY, BUDDY.

04:08.520 --> 04:09.828
- [whispers]
HEY.

04:09.930 --> 04:12.490
- THAT ANGELOU SINKING
THAT BOAT OF HARDSHIP

04:12.590 --> 04:15.764
EXHIBIT ATTITUDE, LOS ANGELES
LATITUDE, LONGITUDE

04:15.870 --> 04:17.838
JESUS AND MY JEWS
FOR MY RELIGION

04:17.940 --> 04:20.079
BOGART A LAN E,
AND THEY GOTI'A MOVE

